io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction

Class LockFundsTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.Transaction
      • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.LockFundsTransaction

  • public class LockFundsTransaction
extends Transaction
    Lock funds transaction is used before sending an Aggregate bonded transaction, as a deposit to announce the transaction. When aggregate bonded transaction is confirmed funds are returned to LockFundsTransaction signer.
    Since:
    1.0
